src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/847941e34e80299a602bc4e5758f43f9.webm?t=1751414136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You also have a TP meter that’ll fill up once you’ve taken or dealt enough damage, allowing you to use that character’s “Special Skill”, to help get you out of a tight spot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you haven’t been sold yet then <span class=\"bb_strike\">get better taste</span> check some of these other key features!:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/353c5a00e0d10ca7660ab21f23382ca6.poster.avif?t=1751414136\" width=144 height=74 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/353c5a00e0d10ca7660ab21f23382ca6.webm?t=1751414136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get run over by a minecart!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/84379834667b42e3517aeab6dd306366.poster.avif?t=1751414136\" width=59 height=115 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/84379834667b42e3517aeab6dd306366.webm?t=1751414136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat up a 15-year old!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/27e8b4ddf0a32a79dc47b19d8d0081eb.poster.avif?t=1751414136\" width=240 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/27e8b4ddf0a32a79dc47b19d8d0081eb.webm?t=1751414136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explosions!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/2b7c860ec933e56fb73c4c0e5582e0f2.poster.avif?t=1751414136\" width=236 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3488200/extras/2b7c860ec933e56fb73c4c0e5582e0f2.webm?t=1751414136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And some other stuff probably!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
